Anshul   Sadana  Chief Customer Officer, Arista Networks, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 1 different industries.40$3,009,346As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Anshul Sadana has been Chief Customer Officer at Arista Networks, Inc since October 4, 2016. Mr. Sadana served as Senior Vice President of Customer Engineering at Arista Networks, Inc. from January 2012 to October 4, 2016. Mr. Sadana served as Vice President of Customer and Systems Engineering of Arista Networks, Inc. He joined Arista in 2007 and is responsible for product definition and development priorities of Arista's next generation products. He also leads all ... systems engineering and customer advocacy functions. He has over a decade of experience in engineering management, design & software development in the networking industry. Previously at Cisco, Mr. Sadana led the development of the Catalyst 4500 and 4900 product lines and also managed strategic customer relations. Mr. Sadana holds an M.S. in Computer Science from the University of Illinois and an M.B.A. from the Wharton School of Business.Read Full Background




