Anshul Sadana



Mr. Anshul Sadana is Chief Customer Officer at Arista Networks, Inc. Mr. Sadana was previously employed as a Principal by Cisco Systems, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Mumbai, a graduate degree from the University of Illinois and an MBA from The Wharton School of the University of Pennsylvania.



